`` you are the weakest link ... '' this vanilla release concludes the final three episodes of the new series of doctor who . boom town is not a fan favorite , but it does have some funny moments . while bad wolf and the parting of the ways ties the season together , starting by putting the doctor , rose and capt jack harkness in reality programs in the future . the new series looks and sounds great . christopher eccleston makes a great doctor , and billie piper is a surprisingly great fit for his doc . 't is a shame eccly only wanted to do one season